OL,7,FA man has been served with an
OL,8,Findictment over the death of a
OL,9,FLockerbie mother-of-two who
OL,10,Fdisappeared nearly 40 years ago.
OL,12,FMarion Hodge was last seen in July
OL,13,F1984 in Dumfries when she was aged 34.
OL,15,FHer body has never been found. She was
OL,16,Fdeclared legally dead by the Court of
OL,17,FSession in Edinburgh, in 1992, with
OL,18,Fthe case being reopened in February of
OL,19,Flast year.
